                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011202-16-off73 t18011202-16-cd74"></join>, six printed books, value 3s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18011202-16-victim191" type="victimName">
                     John 
